CakePhp Code 

1- Select List Code For CakePhp 

echo $this->Form->input('gender', array(
    'options' => array('male' => 'Male', 'female' => 'Female'),
    'empty' => '(choose one)'
));

DES: Add as many options you want

2- Check Box Inside the Form 

echo $this->Form->input('usertype', array('type' => 'checkbox'));

DES: Add the check box For Term and Conditions 

3- Set The value of checkBox As 1 or 0 

echo $this->Form->checkbox('usertype', array(
   'value' => 'Y',
  'hiddenField' => 'N'
));

DES : Check Box Value 

4- Ajax CakePhp Contact Form 
URL : https://github.com/ITHHKN/AjaxCakePHPContactForm.git

DES: Ajax Contact Form Validation 
